track_notes: There are many routes to the top, this one is the least crowded. Dont activate at the summit marker as the Rangers are likely to ask you to stop. There are some flat areas to the north near the radio facility that attract less attention.
Up the hill from Cowles Mountain Tarilhead
Easy start but gets tough at the end. Service road up.
track_title: Up and Down Barker Way Trailhead
